org.eclipse.persistence.jpa.rs.util

Class ConcreteSubclassFactory

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.eclipse.persistence.jpa.rs.util.ConcreteSubclassFactory

  • public class ConcreteSubclassFactory
extends java.lang.Object
    Factory class to create concrete subclasses of abstract classes. This class is used in JPA-RS JAXB mappings to create InstantiationPolicy for abstract classes
    See Also:
    PreLoginMappingAdapter
